_sText:
Completely different map as the BETA version was. 
In this version, you can see the 2nd floor at spawn buildings.
Well, you can only get inside there with a hidden teleport! 

(TIP: Sometimes you have to jump to see how the world looks from up there)

___
Anyways, there is no way going back from secret place, so that might be difficult to server if someone is only camping in secret spot, well, thats easily solved: there is no corner to hide in this map, you can always get shooted from somewhere!
